<div id="aos-EventTabWrapper" class="aos-FL100 aos-OFH aos-PLRM">
<div class="aos-EventTab main aos-FL100 active" data-tabid="1">
<div id="aos-EventLogo" class="aos-FL aos-W33 aos-PRM aos-Br2-W100-KP aos-Br2-P0">
<img loading="lazy" src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;DAM&#x2f;502&#x2f;BBA2024-logo_r38drsd2oqmg.png" alt="The&#x20;British&#x20;Book&#x20;Awards" title="The&#x20;British&#x20;Book&#x20;Awards" class="aos-Image aos-MW100 aos-MBS aos-Br2-W25 aos-Br4-W50" />
</div>
<div id="aos-EventMainInfo" class="aos-FR aos-W66 aos-Br2-W100-KP aos-MB20px">
<div class="aos-FL100 aos-DS38-Intro aos-NL aos-MBS"><p>The British Book Awards is a celebration of books and all who make them.</p></div>
<div class="aos-FL100 aos-DS38-WYSEdit aos-MBM"> <p>It affirms, connects and energises the world of reading by showcasing the authors and illustrators who have stirred our hearts and imaginations, and the industry behind the scenes who have brought them to readers.</p>
<p>It is a demonstration of the creativity, strength, passion and power that are possible when an entire industry unites to connect readers to stories.</p>
<p>Above all it celebrates the intimate connection between the books, their makers and their audience. </p>
<p>Tables and seats are now in very low supply - to check availability, please contact <a href="mailto:paul.clifton@thebookseller.com">paul.clifton@thebookseller.com</a></p>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 1em;">Discover the <a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/awards/the-british-book-awards?tab=book-of-the-year-shortlists">Book of the Year Shortlists</a>.</h3>
<h3 style="margin-bottom: 1em;">Discover the <a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/awards/the-british-book-awards?tab=book-trade-awards-shortlists">Book Trade Shortlists</a>.</h3>
<h3>Key dates for your diary</h3>
<ul class="nibbie-list">
<li><strong>Awards Ceremony</strong>: Monday, 13th May, London &amp; Online</li>
<li><strong>View the livestream:</strong> Available here from 6pm on 13th May</li>
</ul> </div>
</div>
