<div class="aos-CB aos-PTS"><div class="ao-StepByStepCon ao-CrIb aos-StepByStepAwardsStep" data-prev="Previous (Left arrow key)" data-next="Next (Right arrow key)" data-counter="of" data-class="aos-DS38-N"><H3 class="aos-DS38-H3 aos-MTBS ao-StepByStepTitle">Awards Step</H3><div id="ao-Step2235" class="ao-Step100 aos-MBM"><div class="aos-W100"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/529/livestream.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBM" alt="Join us for the livestream" title="Join us for the livestream"></div></div><div id="ao-Step1748" class="ao-Step100 ao-Cr aos-MBM"><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <div class="shortlist-container large"><a class="shortlist-item" href="/awards/the-british-book-awards?tab=book-of-the-year-shortlists"><p>Shortlists</p><h3>Book of the Year</h3></a><a class="shortlist-item" href="/awards/the-british-book-awards?tab=book-trade-awards-shortlists"><p>Shortlists</p><h3>Book Trade Awards</h3></a></div> </div></div><div id="ao-Step2009" class="ao-Step100 ao-Cr"><div class="aos-FL aos-W33 aos-Br2-W50 aos-Br3-W100 aos-PRM ao-Br3-PR0"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/434/Rundell_Katherine__Ben_Turner.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBXS" alt="Katherine Rundell © Ben Turner" title="Katherine Rundell © Ben Turner"><div class="aos-DS38-ImgCaption aos-MBM">Katherine Rundell © Ben Turner</div></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h2>“<em>Winning a Nibbie was a huge joy – a chance to celebrate with people who write, produce and propel books out into the world</em>”</h2><p style="text-align: right;">Katherine Rundell - Winner of Book of the Year: Non-Fiction Narrative 2023<br />for <em>Super-Infinite: The Transformations of John Donne</em></p><p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 20px;"> </p> </div></div></div></div>
