<div class="ao-Article ao-CrIb"><h1 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS38-H1 aos-MBXS aos-W100">Podcasts</h1><div class="aos-Article-IntroText aos-DS38-Intro aos-MBM aos-FL aos-W100"><span class="aos-NL"><p>Nibbies Podcast: from the author’s mind to the reader’s hand</p></span></div><div class="aos-Article-ShareLinks top aos-MBM aos-FL aos-W100 aos-DF aos-DFXpand"><div class="ao-sbcontent" data-clpcode="1" data-itemcode="226508" data-media="0"><div class="ao-sbitems aos-CA aos-DF aos-TAL"><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards&title=Podcasts',600,450,'Linked In');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihLinkedInIcon.svg" alt="Linked&#x20;In" title="Linked&#x20;In" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Podcasts&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards',600,450,'Twitter');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihTwittericon.svg" alt="Twitter" title="Twitter" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https://www.thebookseller.com/awards/the-british-book-awards&t=Podcasts',600,450,'Facebook');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihFBIcon.svg" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span></div></div></div><div class="aos-Article-BodyContainer aos-W100 aos-FL aos-MBS"><div class="aos-Article-MainText aos-DS38-WYSEdit aos-FL100"> <p>Broadcaster &amp; podcast host Hannah MacInnes chats with some of our Nibbies-shortlisted authors about their books, their writing, what’s gone on behind the scenes to get them to where they are, and those lovely moments when they and the books they’ve created have found their readers.</p>
<p>We’ll add new episodes daily, so be sure to check back in or <a href="https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/66140e511f673700170d5295">subscribe to the feed</a>.</p> </div></div><div class="aos-FL100"><code class="aos-DS38-N aos-MBL"><div id="podcast-container">
