ith </span></span><em><span class="TextRun SCXW43653896 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW43653896 BCX8">Cosmopolitan</span></span></em><span class="TextRun SCXW43653896 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW43653896 BCX8"><em> </em>and a takeover at Hay Festival helped bring readers old and new to the series.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW43653896 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"> </span></p> </div></div><div id="ao-Step507" class="ao-Step33 ao-Cr aos-PRM aos-MBM"><div class="aos-W100"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/518/The_Kings_Pants_cover.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="The King's Pants" title="The King's Pants"></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="book-title"><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">The King's Pants</span></h3><h3 class="book-author">Written and illustrated by <span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">Nicholas Allan</span></h3><h4 class="book-publisher"><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">Andersen Press</span></h4><p><span class="TextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8">In celebration of King Charles III’s coronation, Nicholas Allan’s funny picture book </span></span><em><span class="TextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8">The King’s Pants</span></span></em> <span class="TextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="none"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8">benefited</span> </span><span class="TextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW90879012 BCX8">from an award-winning marketing campaign and pant-</