<div class="ao-Article ao-CrIb"><h1 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS38-H1 aos-MBXS aos-W100">Book of the Year - Crime and Thriller</h1><div class="aos-Article-ShareLinks top aos-MBM aos-FL aos-W100 aos-DF aos-DFXpand aos-PTS"><div class="ao-sbcontent" data-clpcode="1" data-itemcode="223429" data-media="0"><div class="ao-sbitems aos-CA aos-DF aos-TAL"><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards&title=Book%20of%20the%20Year%20%2D%20Crime%20and%20Thriller',600,450,'Linked In');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihLinkedInIcon.svg" alt="Linked&#x20;In" title="Linked&#x20;In" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Book%20of%20the%20Year%20%2D%20Crime%20and%20Thriller&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards',600,450,'Twitter');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihTwittericon.svg" alt="Twitter" title="Twitter" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https://www.thebookseller.com/awards/the-british-book-awards&t=Book%20of%20the%20Year%20%2D%20Crime%20and%20Thriller',600,450,'Facebook');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihFBIcon.svg" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span></div></div></div><div class="aos-Article-BodyCon