xtRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing"> and emotional depth of the show. Working with the six authors, who are also the show’s scriptwriters and actors, to a tight timeline, Bloomsbury produced a beautiful, high-spec treasure trove of historical artefacts belonging to the </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">g</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">hosts for readers young and old. It was Bloomsbury’s</span> </span><span class="TextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="none"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">third-</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">bestselling hardback of the year.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW12684922 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"> </span></p> </div></div><div id="ao-Step551" class="ao-Step33 aos-PRM aos-MBM"><div class="aos-W100"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/519/Let_The_Light_Pour_In.jpeg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="Let The Light Pour In" title="Let The Light Pour In"></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="book-title">Let The Light Pour In</h3><h3 class="book-author"><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">Lemn Sissay </span></h3><h4 class="book-publisher"><span class="TextRun SCXW158887410 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW158887410 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing"> Canongate</span></span></h4><p><span class="TextRun SCXW163225444 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW163225444 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">For </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW163225444 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" da