img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/519/Ultra-Processed_People_by_Chris_van_Tulleken_cover.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="Ultra-Processed People: Why Do We All Eat Stuff That Isn’t Food… and Why Can’t We Stop?" title="Ultra-Processed People: Why Do We All Eat Stuff That Isn’t Food… and Why Can’t We Stop?"></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="book-title"><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">Ultra-Processed People</span></h3><h3 class="book-author"><span data-sheets-root="1" data-sheets-value="{" data-sheets-userformat="{">Chris van Tulleken </span></h3><h4 class="book-publisher"><span class="TextRun SCXW9168405 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW9168405 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">Cornerstone Press</span></span></h4><p><span class="TextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">The first book from NHS doctor and presenter Chris van </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">Tulleken</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing"> is an authoritative account of the damage that ultra-processed food (UPF) is doing to our bodies. Cornerstone Press began by </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">establishing</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing"> the author as the expert on UPF, </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="none"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-ccp-parastyle="No Spacing">while </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW181499084 BCX8" data-c