n SCXW242396746 BCX8">here </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8">for the first time in seven years</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8">, having bucked the downward trend in the primary school market with excellent growth. Standouts included its Phonics publishing, which added a non-fiction strand. It outperformed on the trade side too, launching a new home-learning range with </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="none"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8">W</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8">H Smith</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8" lang="EN-GB" xml:lang="EN-GB" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW242396746 BCX8">.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW242396746 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{}"> </span></p> </div></div></div><div class="aos-Article-ShareLinks bottom aos-MBS aos-FL aos-W100 aos-DF aos-DFXpand"><div class="ao-sbcontent" data-clpcode="1" data-itemcode="224253" data-media="0"><div class="ao-sbitems aos-CA aos-DF aos-TAL"><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards&title=Academic%2C%20Educational%20and%20Professional%20Publisher%20of%20the%20Year',600,450,'Linked In');" rel="nofollow"><img src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;Icon&#x2f;Icons&#x2f;17ihLinkedInIcon.svg" alt="Linked&#x20;In" title="Linked&#x20;In" class="aos-Image aos-FL aos-MW100" /></a></span><span class="ao-sbitem aos-FL aos-DF aos-MR5px"><a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="aoOpenDialog('https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Academic%2C%20Educational%20and%20Professional%20Publisher%20of%20the%20Year&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ethebookseller%2Ecom%2Fawards%2Fthe%2Dbritish%2Dbook%2Dawards',600,450,'Twitt