ing.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/515/Lucent_Final_Image.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="Lucent Dreaming" title="Lucent Dreaming"></a></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="grid_head">Lucent Dreaming</h3><h4>Wales</h4><p> </p> </div></div><div id="ao-Step2143" class="ao-Step100 ao-Cr aos-MBM"><H2 class="aos-DS38-H2 aos-MBS HideStepTitle" data-titleshow="1">Finalists</H2></div><div id="ao-Step1661" class="ao-Step100 ao-Cr aos-MBM"><H2 class="aos-DS38-H2 aos-MBS HideStepTitle" data-titleshow="1">East England</H2></div><div id="ao-Step386" class="ao-Step33 ao-Cr aos-PRM aos-MBM"><hr class="aos-FL aos-W100 aos-MBS ao-DS38-HDivider"><div class="aos-W100"><a href="https://www.dedalusbooks.com" target="_blank"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/388/dedalus_for_web.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="Dedalus Books" title="Dedalus Books"></a></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="grid_head">Dedalus Books</h3> </div></div><div id="ao-Step383" class="ao-Step33 aos-PRM aos-MBM"><hr class="aos-FL aos-W100 aos-MBS ao-DS38-HDivider"><div class="aos-W100"><a href="https://www.ueapublishingproject.com" target="_blank"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/515/uea-logo.png" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="UEA Publishing Project " title="UEA Publishing Project "></a></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <h3 class="grid_head">UEA Publishing Project</h3> </div></div><div id="ao-Step381" class="ao-Step33 aos-PRM aos-MBM"><hr class="aos-FL aos-W100 aos-MBS ao-DS38-HDivider"><div class="aos-W100"><a href="https://srlpublishing.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/388/SRL_Publishing_for_web.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="SRL Publishing" title="SRL Publishing"></a></div><div class="aos-DS38-WYSEdit"> <